Class Block

java.lang.Object
Block
Direct Known Subclasses:
AirBlock, IceBlock, LavaBlock, RockBlock, SmogBlock, SoilBlock, WaterBlock
public abstract class Block extends Object
The block superclass that makes the composition of the planet in the bottom left of the game
